---
title: Double Salmon and Gremolata Butter with Broccolini Puttanesca
description: Gremolata -- a sauce of freshly chopped parsley, zingy lemon zest and garlic - is paired with butter to create the ideal accompaniment to pan-fried salmon. It's served with a simple, savoury  broccolini puttanesca.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-double-et-beurre-a-la-gremolata-41f3aea3.jpg
